      "anomaly_id": "L2-003-DUP-001",
      "challenge": "Policy exception for travel_lodging or time-separated reuse",
      "result": "Article 10 is absolute: '同一发票最多报销1次'. No time exception, no expense-type exception, no travel_lodging exception exists in the 2025 policy. The 95-day gap between expense dates does not create a compliant explanation."
    },
    {
      "anomaly_id": "L2-003-DUP-001",
      "challenge": "Budget or threshold boundary",
      "result": "Not a budget/threshold rule — Article 10 is a binary duplicate check. Each claim individually is under AR-01 (<3000). No boundary applies."
    }
